0-installation-script
Step 1: Install Node.js (if not already installed)
Download and install Node.js from the official website: https://nodejs.org/en/download/.

Step 2: Install SASS using npm Install sass -v 3.7.4 if you have node installed:

Step 3: Verify SASS Installation
Run the following command to verify that SASS has been installed correctly:

bash
npx sass --version